fields.name: leftHeight
fields.description: Neo: This variable controls the height of overlays on the left of the hotbar (e.g. health, armor).

fields.name: rightHeight
fields.description: Neo: This variable controls the height of overlays on the right of the hotbar (e.g. food, vehicle health, air).
